In the MATTER OF PROCEEDINGS BY the COMMISSIONER OF BANKING AND INSURANCE, State of New Jersey to Fine Charles Boas Pursuant to the New Jersey Insurance Fraud Prevention Act, N.J.S.A. 17:33A-1 to -30. (Charles Boas - Petitioner) 082693
C-1016 September Term 2018 Supreme Court of New Jersey. JUNE 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002223-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
